  <!-- HOW TO APPLY -->
  <section class="card">
    <h2>How to Apply (Step-by-Step)</h2>
    <ol style="font-size:0.86rem; margin-left:1.2rem;">
      <li>Official portal <strong>rrbapply.gov.in</strong> open karo.</li>
      <li>Apne RRB region select karo (Jaise RRB Ahmedabad, Mumbai, Chennai etc.).</li>
      <li>New registration karke basic details, qualification, category, address fill karo.</li>
      <li>Photo, signature aur required documents upload karo (size &amp; format jaise notification me hai).</li>
      <li>Application fee online pay karo (UPI / net banking / card).</li>
      <li>Final submit ke baad application form ka print/save rakh lo.</li>
    </ol>
    <div class="btn-row">
